name: CampusCultr
overview:
CampusCultr is an educational brand.

The vision of CampusCultr is to be pioneer in bringing an educational revolution and to make education fun and motivated. It is also a voice that calls for unification of talent, resources and technology to making learning better.

CampusCultr at present works with College Fests and helps the promotion of college events and also partners with them on various levels. College events are an excellent platform to bring the learning culture and hence it works closely with such events.

It also runs a online magazine, Campulse that provides insightful information and resources in form of tutorials. Campulse is in short a guide, resource platform for College students.
